Package com.flipkart.business

Interface GymCentreServiceInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GymCentreService
    public interface GymCentreServiceInterface
    This interface defines the service operations related to Gym Centre functionality. It includes methods for retrieving gym centers by owner ID and city, getting available slots by center and date, adding a new gym center, requesting gym center approval, and retrieving gym center details by ID.
